org.apache.karaf.bundle.command.bundletree

Class Tree<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.karaf.bundle.command.bundletree.Node<T>
      • org.apache.karaf.bundle.command.bundletree.Tree<T>

  • public class Tree<T>
extends Node<T>

    Represent a tree that can be written to the console.

    The output will look like this: 
     root
 +- child1
 |  +- grandchild
 +- child2
